\c 17 dziva pamusoro penzombe dzendarira dzakanga dziri pasi paro, akariisa pachigadziko chamabwe. 18 Nenzira, yaiva nedenga, yakaitirwa imba yezororo, yavakanga vavaka temberi, nomukova wamambo nechokunze, wakazvishandura mukati metemberi yaJehovha, nokuda kwamambo weAsiria. 19 Zvino mamwe mabasa aAhazi aakaita, hazvina kunyorwa here mubhuku yamakoronike amadzibaba aJudha? 20 Ahazi akavata namadzibaba ake, akavigwa muguta raDhavhidhi, Hezekia mwanakomana wake akamutevera paushe.
